<p>The <b>Ontario Provincial Police</b> (<b>O.P.P.</b>) (<a href="/wiki/French_language" title="French language">French</a>: <span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr"><i>Police provinciale de l'Ontario</i></span>) is the <a href="/wiki/State_police" title="State police">Provincial Police service</a> for the province of <a href="/wiki/Ontario" title="Ontario">Ontario</a>, <a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada">Canada</a>.</p>
<p></p>
